# inradius

- _inradius(aGeometry)_

Answer the radius of the incircle of _aGeometry_.

At `Triangle`:

```
>>> sssTriangle(3, 4, 5).inradius
1
```

At `Rectangle`:

```
>>> Rectangle([0 0], [1 1]).inradius
1/2
```

